document_data.Notable Owners:
* [[Mhzentul]], creator of the Seven Lost Rings.
* [[Whisper]], a Zhentarim wizard who found several of the rings after Mhzentul's death.
* [[Ceryx]], a [[fire elementalist]] who ''nearly'' recovered two of the rings from Whisper, but was beaten to the punch by Doust Soulwood.{{Cite card/AD&D Trading Cards/1993|309|[[Ceryx]]}}
